  "title": "Cleaning Supervisor (Integrated Resort/ 4 days work per week/ Harbour Front)",
  "description": "<h2>Company Overview</h2><p>Our client operates within a <strong>large-scale, service-oriented integrated resort environment</strong> and is committed to maintaining high standards of hygiene, safety, and customer experience. They are currently seeking a <strong>hands-on Cleaning Supervisor</strong> to support daily operations and lead frontline teams.</p><h2>Job Summary</h2><p>Supervise daily cleaning operations and lead frontline staff to ensure hygiene, safety, and service standards in an integrated resort.</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Supervise and carry out cleaning and sanitation works in accordance with SOP and safety requirements</p></li><li><p>Ensure proper use of PPE, cleaning chemicals, and equipment</p></li><li><p>Plan manpower deployment and oversee daily operations and productivity</p></li><li><p>Conduct inspections and audits to maintain cleanliness and service standards</p></li><li><p>Train, coach, and guide cleaning staff to meet contractual requirements</p></li><li><p>Maintain cleaning records, reports, and logs</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with workplace safety, health, and environmental procedures</p></li><li><p>Uphold professional grooming standards and customer service etiquette</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>2-3 years’ experience as a Cleaning Supervisor</p></li><li><p>Strong leadership and communication skills</p></li><li><p>Hands-on and willing to support operations when required</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working 12-hour shifts (4 days work per week)</p></li></ul><p><strong>How to Apply</strong><br />If you are interested, please submit your updated resume by clicking the <strong>Apply Now</strong> button.</p><p><em>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>Lee Yu Qian (Lenore)</p><p>Registration Number: R24124538</p><p>EA License Number:18C9027</p>",
